---
title: Philly Cheesesteak Pizza with Side Salad
description: A fun twist on a Philly classic. Pastrami-spiced steak strips and top cheesy pizzas with classic green bell peppers.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/philly-cheesesteak-pizza-1e114d38.jpg
